videos.headline: C. Virgil pass,to K. Johnson for 36 yds for a TD
videos.description: Chason Virgil pass complete to KeeSean Johnson for 36 yds for a TD

videos.headline: C. Virgil pass,to J. Jordan for 58 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Chason Virgil pass complete to Jamire Jordan for 58 yds to the AFA 22 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Johnson's second TD is a spinning thing of beauty
videos.description: With one TD already on the board, KeeSean Johnson makes his second of the highlight variety spinning around to catch the fade and stay in bounds increasing Fresno State's lead to 14-0.

videos.headline: Air Force DB takes to the sky for spectacular end zone INT
videos.description: Chason Virgil's pass into the end zone gets deflected into the air where Brodie Hicks decides to soar through the air for the amazing interception for Air Force.

videos.headline: Hicks picks off Virgil for the second time
videos.description: Chason Virgil pass intercepted Brodie Hicks return for 30 yds to the AFA 49

videos.headline: Cleveland breaks off defenders for a 33-yard TD
videos.description: Nate Romine pass complete to Ronald Cleveland for 33 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Healy with the pick-six to give Air Force its first lead of the game
videos.description: Chason Virgil pass intercepted for a TD Patrick Healy return for 35 yds for a TD

videos.headline: C. Virgil pass,to K. Johnson for 52 yds for a TD
videos.description: Chason Virgil pass complete to KeeSean Johnson for 52 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Worthman's TD run puts Air Force ahead for good
videos.description: Fresno State jumps out early on Air Force, but the Falcons fight back and finally take the lead with Arion Worthman's two-yard run and hold on for the win.

videos.headline: Steelhammer adds name to list of diving Air Force interceptions
videos.description: With Fresno State driving, Weston Steelhammer makes the incredible diving interception off a deflected pass to stop the Bulldogs and preserve the Falcons' lead.

videos.headline: Fresno State defense denies Air Force on 4th & goal
videos.description: Jacobi Owens run for a loss of 3 yards to the FrsSt 4

videos.headline: Worthman keeps it for his second rushing TD
videos.description: Arion Worthman run for 4 yds for a TD
